  "summary": {
    "en": "A colorful DIY fort kit with multiple rods and connector balls for building houses, towers, tunnels, and activity frames.",
    "zh": "彩色DIY堡垒拼搭套装，配有多色杆件和连接球，可搭建房屋、高塔、通道和活动框架。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 120-piece set supports open-ended fort building for homes, classrooms, playrooms, and family activity programs.",
      "Five-color poles and two-color connector balls create a bright retail look while helping children recognize structure and sequence.",
      "The reusable plastic system encourages hands-on construction, spatial thinking, cooperation, and imaginative role play.",
      "Custom color matching, logo, manual, and color-box packaging can be discussed for OEM/ODM and private-label projects."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "120件套适合家庭、教室、游戏室和亲子活动项目中的开放式堡垒拼搭。",
      "五色杆件与双色连接球形成明亮的零售视觉，也有助于儿童识别结构和拼接顺序。",
      "可重复使用的塑料拼接系统鼓励动手建构、空间思维、协作和角色扮演。",
      "可根据OEM/ODM和自有品牌项目需求沟通颜色、Logo、说明书和彩盒包装定制。"
    ]
  },
